race.comment: TALENT SCOUT (10) is second up off a short break. He came back a furlong in trip last start with the gap between runs and ran very well for a narrow fourth over 1600m. Prior to that he'd started $2.80 in the Listed Hill Smith Stakes in Adelaide behind the likes of Freedom Flame & Different Gravy. He'll cross over here and take plenty of catching. DIVINE THOUGHTS (6) has been solid in three runs this time in and looks ideally suited getting to 2000m fourth up being by So You Think. VIZIE (8) can mix her form but was good over this route last time and can figure again. MACY MOON (2) mixes his form a bit but was close up last time and has claims on that.
